Design and develop a vibrant, user-friendly full-stack web application that empowers marketing teams to launch, manage, and analyze campaigns with ease. The app should feature a visually engaging dashboard, campaign creation tools, real-time analytics, and seamless integration with social media platforms. Prioritize intuitive UX, responsive design, and scalability. The tone should be energetic and brand-positive, with delightful micro-interactions that make users feel excited and in control of their marketing success.
